Spartacus's wrath.

04:58.131 --> 05:00.463
Gannicus: A thing that threatens
to consume many innocent lives.

05:00.634 --> 05:02.795
Gallienus: We have thought you
but mangled corpse

05:02.969 --> 05:05.460
