down upon you,

26:27.419 --> 26:28.579
and yet here you stand,

26:28.754 --> 26:31.996
a phoenix
risen from its ashes.

26:33.717 --> 26:35.753
The gods have truly
blessed him.

26:35.928 --> 26:38.419
