27:00.619 --> 27:02.610
yet can hold value.

27:05.791 --> 27:08.498
Your rudis.

27:09.628 --> 27:11.289
And its price?

27:11.463 --> 27:13.454
A simple oath

27:13.632 --> 27:15.463
pledging yourself
to my command.

27:18.679 --> 27:20.965
Lucretia

27:21.140 --> 27:23.973
