victim of Spartacus

27:24.143 --> 27:26.384
yet now stands
a powerful symbol

27:26.562 --> 27:29.474
used to calm
swelling concern.

27:29.648 --> 27:31.980
I would add you as such--

27:32.151 --> 27:35.268
a former slave
of the House of Batiatus

27:35.445 --> 27:38.653
now sworn to bring
errant brothers to justice.

27:38.824 --> 27:40.985
It appears you already have
one of those.

27:43.453 --> 27:46.069
